    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302092</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;さん、&lt;Mel&gt;さん、
どうもお久しぶりです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, &lt;Mel&gt;. It has been a while.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302136</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>久しぶり！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Been too long!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302184</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>元気だった？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How are you doing?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302236</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>はい、おかげさまで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have been blessed with good health.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302336</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ご報告します</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chief, we've got a report!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302336</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;方面は、
我が部隊で固めました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The area around &lt;Red&gt;Euclid&lt;White&gt; has been reinforced!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302412</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ご苦労様です。
もう少し様子を
見ましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There seems to be a predicament. Very well, I will look into it in a moment.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302504</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……相変わらず、
&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃんは頭領の仕事で
忙しいんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Some things never change. I guess she has to attend to her duties as ninja chief.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302584</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……だね。わたしたち、
お邪魔みたい、行こ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah... I think we're going to bother her if we stay. Let's go...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302676</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;さん？　&lt;Mel&gt;さん？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;...? &lt;Mel&gt;...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302676</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……行ってしまわれたのですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...They have already taken their leave...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302916</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あなたの本当の心は
まだ闇の中にある……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your real feelings are still engulfed in darkness...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302916</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>正気を失っていたとは言え、
実の両親に手をかけた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You must lose your true character if you wish to take over the work of your parents...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302916</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>それには正当な理由が
あったのかもしれない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet that, perhaps, is not the real motive of your actions...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302916</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>でも、あの時の刃の重みは。
両親を斬った時に手に感じた
鈍い重みは消えない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But it is of no matter... The weight of that blade you used that time is always in your hands...Yes, the blade you used to mercilessly behead your father and mother. That weight becomes no lighter with the passage of time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
