      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303120</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>泣いてもいいのよ。
何かのせいにして、
泣き叫んでも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's ok to cry. You can tell them it was someone else's fault.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303120</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>非情な掟を強いる、こんな
境遇など全部、放り出して
彼らについていっても</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is a place heartlessness prevails. Abandon this ruthless place you aren't allowed to feel anything and join them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
