    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305492</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>非情な掟を強いる、こんな
境遇など全部、放り出して
彼らについていっても</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is a place heartlessness prevails. Abandon this ruthless place you aren't allowed to feel anything and join them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303328</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>人はみな心に傷を隠し持って
生きてゆくものです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everyone hides feelings they would rather express openly in hopes to avoid hurting. Living means such.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303328</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>泣き叫んでも、怒っても
自分より勝る者を妬んでも、
傷は癒えるはずもありません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if I screamed and cried. Even if I became angry. Even if I outlawed for my own sake. The wounds will not simply vanish. It would be childish to expect so.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303328</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あなたもそれを
わかっているのでは
ないのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it that you simply do not understand such a thing?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303380</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>キレイごとを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Such beautiful things you are neglecting...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305548</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>キレイごとを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Such beautiful things you are neglecting...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303452</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>また&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃんに
近付きやがって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stay away from &lt;Suzu&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303500</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>退きなさい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Get away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303548</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……ふん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mph...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305600</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……ふん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mph...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303608</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>平気！？
何もされてない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you ok!? Did she hurt you...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303688</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ええ、わたしは……
でも、どうして戻って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I am fine...But I do not understand why you returned...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303764</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>友達のピンチに
駆けつけなくて
どーすんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can't just leave a friend in trouble alone!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303808</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>友達……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Friend...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303884</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>前に言ったでしょ、
わたしたち、友達だって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I said it before, we're friends.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303952</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……ふふふ……
そうでしたね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Hahahaha...Is that so.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304052</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……わたし、おふたりと
ご一緒させていただいて、
いいでしょうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is it acceptable if I accompany you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304128</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>え……でも、
&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃんは里のことが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...B-but &lt;Suzu&gt;, what about your work?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304220</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>私の助けが必要で、
ここまでいらしたのでは
ないのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you have come all the way here it must be to ask for my help. Is that not the case?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304280</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……一緒に来てくれるか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...So you'll be coming with us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304408</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>もちろん。おふたりには
ご迷惑をおかけしましたし、
ご恩もあります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>By all means. I am obligated to help you after all the help you have provided.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304408</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>それに……『友達』ですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To reciprocate...that is what "friends" do, correct?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304464</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと、&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks, &lt;Suzu&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304524</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>後のことは、
任せました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I shall protect your backs.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>47</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304580</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>は……ご健闘を</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>G-good luck out there, chief!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>48</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304632</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>んじゃあ、行くぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ok, let's go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>49</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304728</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>この闇はいつまでも
晴れることはないでしょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is true I will never clear the cloudiness of my heart.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>50</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304728</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>それでも私は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nevertheless I...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>50</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
